<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Gen Z</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include ../partials/_menu %>
  <main class="wrapper case-study genz">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Gen Z</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Connecting the&nbsp;<br />brightest minds of&nbsp;<br />today and tomorrow</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Mentoring Social Platform</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We designed a web application that links students and recent graduates with real professionals, giving careers a jump start.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded gray">
      <div class="container row between">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            A fresh interface for both students and professionals
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            How do you get millennials and anyone over 35 to agree that something is cool?
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            A modern platform designed for all users
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            Weaving in the best of modern trends with smart, intuitive information brings everyone together.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Brand System</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Interaction Design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Functional, as well as beautiful</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            We started with information architecture to establish functionality before applying visual design, making the interface as beautiful as it is usable.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block padded-top column half-md red">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="174" data-height="150">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/genz/agenda.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-bottom">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded dark-blue">
      <div class="container row">
        <div class="inner-block column half-md two-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop shadow sr-left lazy-ratio" data-width="1603" data-height="1309">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/genz/coaches.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column order-top-xs half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">An organized life for students</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Students and recent graduates can find everything they need in a central location and via the universal navigation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top gray">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content padded-bottom gutter-right">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Attention to detail from every side</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              We ensure that mentors also feel at home in the interface and catered to their interests with relevant statistics and a custom scheduler.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column align-bottom half-md">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="229" data-height="150">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/genz/card-1.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/genz/card-2.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-bottom">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/genz/card-3.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-bottom">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img data-normal="./images/work/genz/laptop.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block padded">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Skimming by cards</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              The interface uses cards as an organization tool to improve skimmability. Users can quickly sort through information presented to them.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column half-md">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="239" data-height="150">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/genz/stats.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-right">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral centered row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column red">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
          <p class="case-referral-text centered">&ldquo;The Brave team brings an impressive depth of knowledge and experience to the table. Each time we met, they presented excellent work and had inspiring ideas and insights to contribute. They were invaluable partners every step of the way.&rdquo;</p>
          <p class="case-referral-author">Doug Anderson, <em>Founder, Gen Z Connect</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-block padded">
      <a href="./work/foh" class="cta-button cta-button-left" title="Previous Case">Previous Case</a>
      <div class="cta-content container">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="cta-text">Sometimes, you find something that just works.</div>
          <a href="/approach" class="btn btn-text icon-arrow">See Our Approach</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="./work/cityhealth" class="cta-button cta-button-right" title="Next Case">Next Case</a>
    </section>

    <%- include ../partials/_footer %>
  </main>

  <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>
</html>
